Automated tests for rrplayer-fc

These are integration tests, and expect a RR instore box-like environment.

SETTING UP FOR TESTS

 - Make sure that pg ident logins will work (check your pg_hba.conf)

 - Create a database user, eg:

    sudo -U postgres psql
    CREATE USER david;

 - Create a schedule database to test with, eg:

    CREATE DATABASE schedule_test WITH TEMPLATE schedule;

 - Grant permissions required for the tests, eg:

    \c schedule_test
    GRANT INSERT, SELECT ON tblinstore_media TO david;
    GRANT UPDATE ON tblinstore_media_lnginstore_media_seq TO david;
    GRANT INSERT, SELECT ON tblinstore_media_dir TO david;
    GRANT UPDATE ON tblinstore_media_dir_lnginstore_media_dir_seq TO david;
